description: Taoiseach Leo Varadkar confirms the country will move to phase three of its lockdown roadmap.
title: Coronavirus: Ireland to further ease restrictions on Monday
title_page: Coronavirus: Ireland to further ease restrictions on Monday - BBC News
maintext: "We must now try and repair the damage that has been done, across all parts of our lives, and show the same solidarity in doing so," Mr Varadkar continued.
